{"tid":1312511,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人以為兔子冇感情無視主人, 其實完全相反......","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T17:41:14.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf996d11db696c488b8b4b215bea914e3c21989","tid":1312511,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n無視主人的誤會而被棄養：其實兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。兔子也有遠視。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n以下2個videos可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=42f18ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=1d7d7b59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子的行為解釋網站：</span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協: <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=c826967d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站): <a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=c5881209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂): <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=1ddbacb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"5667c215b9a1017c53aced997064cc76f03ffb12","tid":1312511,"uid":212274,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:08:35.000Z","msg":"起底發現樓主應該係外國公司研究既AI黎，靜係出兔仔post以免太引人注目呢招算醒，有唔少post d語氣唔自然，不過都最近都叫有進步，有心做中文語系做成咁算唔錯，請繼續加油。"},{"pid":"b36c596790dc0bf4a60fedc81ffff9d9f2fc34c7","tid":1312511,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5667c215b9a1017c53aced997064cc76f03ffb12","tid":1312511,"uid":212274,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:08:35.000Z","msg":"起底發現樓主應該係外國公司研究既AI黎，靜係出兔仔post以免太引人注目呢招算醒，有唔少post d語氣唔自然，不過都最近都叫有進步，有心做中文語系做成咁算唔錯，請繼續加油。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"但佢有時會入tvb post用英文講啲關於選美既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eda0ddd5e3b1e8e14bb39df79bcd3c27c1645a","tid":1312511,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5667c215b9a1017c53aced997064cc76f03ffb12","tid":1312511,"uid":212274,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:08:35.000Z","msg":"起底發現樓主應該係外國公司研究既AI黎，靜係出兔仔post以免太引人注目呢招算醒，有唔少post d語氣唔自然，不過都最近都叫有進步，有心做中文語系做成咁算唔錯，請繼續加油。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}